ht: 541.5pt; width: 53.25pt;\" width=\"71\" x:str=\"\">138元</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr height=\"90\">\r\n	<td class=\"et17\" height=\"90\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0.5pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 67.5pt; width: 99pt;\" width=\"132\" x:str=\"\">内科</td>\r\n	<td class=\"et18\" height=\"90\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0.5pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 67.5pt; width: 234pt;\" width=\"312\" x:str=\"\">通过视、触、叩、听等体格检查方法，检查心、肺、肝、脾等重要脏器及神经系统基本情况，发现内科常见疾病。</td>\r\n	<td class=\"et19\" height=\"90\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0.5pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 67.5pt; width: 40.5pt;\" width=\"54\" x:num=\"3\">3</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr height=\"90\">\r\n	<td class=\"et17\" height=\"90\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0.5pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 67.5pt; width: 99pt;\" width=\"132\" x:str=\"\">外科</td>\r\n	<td class=\"et18\" height=\"90\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0.5pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 67.5pt; width: 234pt;\" width=\"312\" x:str=\"\">检查皮肤、甲状腺、骨关节、肛肠、乳腺等重要脏器基本情况，发现常见外科疾病的重要征兆，或初步排除外科常见疾病。</td>\r\n	<td class=\"et19\" height=\"90\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0.5pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 67.5pt; width: 40.5pt;\" width=\"54\" x:num=\"3\">3</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr height=\"43\">\r\n	<td class=\"et16\" height=\"296\" rowspan=\"6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border-wid